FeedPackage.Description: Adds Sass processing capability to SquishIt. Can compile .sass and .scss files. SASS compilation uses the interpreter in the SassAndCoffee project, which does not support all SASS features (e.g. placeholder classes). Use this package if you require SASS support. If you only require SCSS support, consider using SquishIt.NSass, which uses a faster compiler and has better feature support.
